From 7ef80a90e0aa99ab76027b55937acca2a1a7c468 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Olamidotuniy <olamidotun225@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 18 Feb 2026 14:48:22 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 4/8] feat: enhance GraphQL error handling and logging

- Added detailed error parsing and mapping to GraphQL error codes in graphql-ws.ts.
- Implemented request ID extraction from headers for better traceability.
- Introduced a GraphQL plugin for logging errors with context information.
- Updated context handling in GraphQL configuration to include request ID.

feat: update marketplace shipment bid DTOs

- Made awardedByProfileId and providerId fields optional in AwardShipmentBidDto and CreateShipmentBidDto respectively.
- Introduced MarketplaceShipmentsFilterDto for filtering marketplace shipments.

feat: implement marketplace shipments query

- Added marketplaceShipments query to MarketPlaceResolver with filtering capabilities.
- Implemented marketplaceShipments method in MarketPlaceService to handle shipment retrieval with filters.
- Enhanced shipment bid handling with user context in various resolver methods.

feat: extend GraphQL types and schema

- Added new types for marketplace shipments results and vehicle details.
- Updated existing types to include new fields such as pickupAddressSummary and dropoffAddressSummary.
- Modified schema.gql to reflect changes in input and output types for marketplace functionalities.

feat: integrate vehicle management in shipments service

- Implemented vehicle retrieval logic in ShipmentsService for provider dashboard.
- Added vehicle mapping to GraphQL types for better integration with existing shipment data.
